edge: In the movie, Anshul 'Gogo' Sharma and Tarun Thakur are two characters portrayed by Kartik Aaryan and Omkar Kapoor respectively.
Both Anshul 'Gogo' Sharma and Siddharth 'Sid' Gandotra / Chauka are characters played by Kartik Aaryan in the movie.
Ruchika 'Chiku' Khanna and Supriya Randhawa are portrayed by Nushrat Bharucha and Sonnalli Seygall in the movie.
Kusum Singh is played by Ishita Raj Sharma while Supriya Randhawa is played by Sonnalli Seygall in the movie.
Supriya Randhawa, portrayed by Sonnalli Seygall in the movie, is the daughter of Rakesh Randhawa played by Sharat Saxena.
Supriya Randhawa, portrayed by Sonnalli Seygall in the movie, is the daughter of Mrs. Randhawa played by Mona Ambegaonkar.
Sunny, portrayed by Manvir Singh in the movie, is the best friend of Chiku played by Prakhar Shukla.
Ruchi and Chiku's best friend are both portrayed by Rumana Molla in the movie.
Tina is also one of Chiku's best friends, portrayed by Karishma Sharma in the movie.
Raju, played by Rajan in the movie, is a gift delivery man.
Aparshakti Khurana appears as an unnamed character, 'Man in Bathroom', in the movie.
